_sText:
Cliffdiver
cs_cdiver

Map by MarkQ/Turd Furguson

Candy is usually intended to be a thing of joy and happiness.
Never before has such an innocent treat become such a twisted tool 
of desire. Four high-clearance weapons scientists, all with nuclear, 
chemical or biological backgrounds, had a desire for tasty, tasty candy. 
Upon learning of a complex that harboured delicious candy, 
they boarded their shared winnebago and journeyed to the cliffside. 
However, when they got there all they found were bloodthirsty terrorists
who put them in a control room where all they could do was stand around. 
Counter Terrorists have been informed and are enroute.

HDR RE-RELEASE, with bot pathing and graphical bugs fixed.

ANY BUGS/SUGGESTIONS, PLEASE EMAIL ME AT: sniperx87@hotmail.com

credits: MarkQ, Valve for the models/textures.
